Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.50,0:00:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.29,0:00:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,金奖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.31,0:00:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得了金奖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我去告诉麻美
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.97,0:00:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,她紧张得躲在洗手间里不敢出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.45,0:00:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,在这些学校之中 将参加关西大赛的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.58,0:00:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是金奖…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然是「无用金奖」 但也是金奖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.00,0:00:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,高坂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.24,0:00:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,高兴得都哭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,拿了金奖 太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.65,0:01:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.16,0:01:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,实在是不甘心得要死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.12,0:01:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么拿了「无用金奖」大家还能开心得起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.06,0:01:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的目标不是全国大赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.04,0:01:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的觉得我们有实力进入全国大赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.68,0:01:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.73,0:01:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你没觉得不甘心？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.81,0:01:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,非常不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.31,0:01:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我会相信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.94,0:02:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,「上了高中 胸部就会变大」这种说法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.72,0:02:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.22,0:02:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,在我想着这种事情的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.87,0:02:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我的高中生活已快要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.38,0:02:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,故意选了这所初中同学很少的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.90,0:02:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为只有这里的制服是自己憧憬的水手服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.74,0:02:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 想让许多事情 回归零点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.57,0:02:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,各位新同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.34,0:02:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到北宇治高中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是吹奏乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.77,0:02:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,为了祝贺光彩照人的各位的入学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.46,0:03:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这不行啊…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,--------------------------------------------------Part A--------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,实在太烂了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,一点都不整齐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,音准和节奏也错误百出
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 也不像是以全国大赛为目标的样子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.35,0:05:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 的确是烂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你指什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚刚不是说了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.45,0:05:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,「的确是烂啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.02,0:05:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我说出来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,话说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.05,0:05:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我吗？加藤叶月
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.40,0:05:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,就坐在你后面 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.17,0:05:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫黄前久美子 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 究竟是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,回到各自座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,都上高中了还在教室里吵吵闹闹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.34,0:05:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,实在不是什么值得称赞的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你们裙子的长度是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,快弄回原样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.64,0:06:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我是这个一年级三班的班主任松本美知惠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,先点个名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,麻井雄大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,石川有纪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.46,0:06:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,内山田弘子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,江口阳子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,黄前久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.37,0:06:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,加藤叶月
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.83,0:06:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,川岛…绿…辉？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.42,0:06:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…应该读sapphire
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:33.80,Tips,,0,0,0,,注：蓝宝石之意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,绿色的绿 光辉的辉 读作sapphire
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,川岛…绿 辉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(704,660)\fs30}sapphire
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.22,0:06:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}sapphire吗 真帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 不会再念错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,久美子 一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 久美子？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,名字 没叫错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…嗯 没叫错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.32,0:06:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,就叫我叶月吧 或者加藤之类的也行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,随便叫就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有一起回家的伙伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.83,0:07:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 我决定要在高中交到新朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.81,0:07:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,体验许多新鲜的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,所以请多指教啦 久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:19.33,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(740,480)\fad(500,0)\blur2}欢　迎　来　到　高　中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 到底是什么烂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.67,0:07:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那个就别提…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.98,0:07:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,opal酱！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:25.76,Tips,,0,0,0,,注：欧泊石（一般为乳白色）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不对啦 好像是更像绿色的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.99,0:07:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,请问 请问请问
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.04,0:07:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那个是大号君对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,大号君真可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.13,0:07:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.13,0:07:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我能摸一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.87,0:07:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 opal酱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.33,0:07:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是绿辉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.33,0:07:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(660,660)\fs30}sapphire
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.53,0:07:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,绿辉酱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(618,660)\fs30}sapphire
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.28,0:07:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你很喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,真可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.95,0:07:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是大号形状的吉祥物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,大号？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是一种铜管乐器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,铜管乐器？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.27,0:07:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,绿以前是吹奏乐部的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是拉低音提琴的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.01,0:08:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,低音提琴？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,绿？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,「绿」就是绿的名字啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,sapphire总觉得有些那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.97,0:08:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,要是能叫我「绿」的话我会很感激的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 低音提琴是乐器的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,有这——么大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,就像是小提琴变成了大怪物那样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我见过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.03,0:08:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前也是吹奏乐部的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.69,0:08:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.25,0:08:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.10,0:08:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,黄…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,黄前久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.06,0:08:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,叫久美子就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫叶月
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,久美子…久美子所属的声部是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.76,0:08:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 低音部 我是吹悠风号的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.47,0:08:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此 你很有那种感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.64,0:08:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 幽浮？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.24,0:08:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不是幽浮是悠风号
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.14,0:08:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是叫做悠风号的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.14,0:08:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(660,660)\fs30}Euphonium
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 就是这个的缩小版
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.35,0:08:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 那还真是小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.00,0:09:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我啊 到初中为止都是网球部的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,上了高中后想学学吹奏乐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,绿正打算去吹奏乐部参观呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,方便的话 大家一起去怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:12.69,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(660,372)\fs50\c&H515A52&}欢 迎 来 到 吹 奏 乐 部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:12.69,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(740,450)\fs40\c&H515A52&\fn方正宋一_GBK\b1}向着音乐教室GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.30,0:09:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那是小号吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.93,0:09:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我想吹那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.43,0:09:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,很帅气对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.32,0:09:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,快看快看 叶月
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.90,0:09:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是悠风号
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.13,0:09:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,哪个哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 悠风号好大！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,都怪久美子说比大号君还小的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 对不起啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.98,0:09:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,萨克斯也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,叶月？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.48,0:09:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 你们难道是来参观的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.86,0:09:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,快 进来进来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on！Join us！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.58,0:09:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 好漂亮啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,来来来 这里就是我校的吹奏乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.42,0:10:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是参观者第一号
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,作为纪念 给你们吃糖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.34,0:10:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.45,0:10:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,因为会让新生感到紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,所以不是说好不要去搭话的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.12,0:10:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.34,0:10:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你看她们已经害怕起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 请慢慢参观吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.29,0:10:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好了快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.12,0:10:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,铜奖…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.90,0:10:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.02,0:10:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那个方形的东西是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 那是调谐器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.21,0:10:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是用来调音的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.22,0:10:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 难道说你是初学者？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那就从吹奏乐最基础的部分开始教…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,0:10:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,明 日 香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:10:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.90,0:11:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那就先用B调调音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,长号 注意跟上节奏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,圆号 音准偏了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,注意听吹出的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,再来一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,可以用调谐器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.29,0:11:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.69,0:11:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,音调有些偏了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,高坂同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.86,0:11:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是来参观的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 我想申请入部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.77,0:11:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到吹奏乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,梨子 快去拿入部申请表
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.22,0:11:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 现在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:12:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,当然了 要是她跑掉了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.02,0:12:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,又不是小猫…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多该走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.93,0:12:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才那个女生好漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你认识她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.09,0:12:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 啊…不能说认识
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,初中时我和她都是吹奏乐部的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那不就是认识嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…也不是很熟啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 这间学校吹奏乐部的水平
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}久美子好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.41,0:12:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,比想象的…怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:47.91,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(594,580)\fs30\fscx80\fn方正宋一_GBK\b1\bord1\blur2\c&H4D47C9&\3c&H000000&\frz12.8}请　按　下　按　钮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,还要糟糕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.27,0:12:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,大概是以在府大会上获得银奖为目标吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:51.62,Tips,,0,0,0,,注：京都府
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.69,0:12:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,银奖不是很厉害吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,要是想在关西 或是全国大赛上出场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.91,0:13:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,就必须在各地区的大赛上获得金奖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.06,0:13:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 即使得了金奖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是「无用金奖」也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,无用…无用金奖是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:13.06,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\move(888,538,720,538)\fs50\c&H513D3C&\3c&HAD75C2&\4c&H8E78B6&\bord1\shad2}新手·老手……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:13.06,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\move(940,610,772,610)\fs50\c&H513D3C&\3c&HAD75C2&\4c&H8E78B6&\bord1\shad2}欢迎任何人！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:13.06,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\move(1008,672,840,672)\fs30\c&H833B18&}特别是\N　男生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.30,0:13:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,吹奏乐大赛分金银铜三级奖项
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,从获得金奖的队伍中选出继续参赛的代表队
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,没有被选上的队伍获得的就叫「无用金奖」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,就像绿辉说的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,660)\fs30}sapphire
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,如果想继续参赛的话 「无用金奖」是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.36,0:13:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 很难懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.12,0:13:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.39,0:13:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 我们三个加入的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.59,0:13:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不就会成为救世主吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,没那么简单啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.97,0:13:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,绿要参加
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.31,0:13:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,因为绿喜欢音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.44,0:13:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,绿坚信 无论何时何地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.02,0:13:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,音乐都是能够打动人心的强大语言之一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.71,0:13:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,信号灯 半天也不变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.63,0:13:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是绿忘记按按钮了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.03,0:13:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,靠谱一点啦 绿辉酱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:13:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是绿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,久美子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,打算参加吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,吹奏乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.81,0:14:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,再稍微考虑一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.81,0:14:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,电车来了 那我走这边了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.15,0:14:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你之前说「烂」 是指吹奏乐部吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,--------------------------------------------------Part B--------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.31,0:14:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.68,0:14:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么高坂同学会在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.19,0:14:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,她那么厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.53,0:15:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,还以为她去了洛秋或者立华呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.36,0:15:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,真是失误…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.99,0:15:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,呦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是秀一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.86,0:15:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 对青梅竹马连个招呼都不打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,明明都在同一间学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.03,0:15:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,头发扎起来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.45,0:15:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.66,0:15:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来高坂丽奈也在这儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我说你…反应是不是有些迟钝？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.01,0:15:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是你叫我别跟你说话的 我只是听你的话罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.52,0:15:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,初三的时候你不是跟我说过「丑女别跟我说话」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…那是因为你在大家的面前问我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.16,0:15:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,「今天要来我家吃饭吗」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不对 现在不是说这个的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,社团你打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.19,0:15:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,还没决定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:15:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不去吹奏乐部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:15:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.63,0:16:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我也没有其他想做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.37,0:16:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,大概就去吹奏乐部…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.30,0:16:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不去吹奏乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然之前想去 但现在决定不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.18,0:16:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,为啥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不为啥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.92,0:16:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,她是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.05,0:16:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.41,0:16:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啦 你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,高中怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.13,0:16:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…马马虎虎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐在回来的路上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.61,0:16:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,来帮忙准备晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.42,0:16:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,吹奏乐部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的觉得我们有实力进入全国大赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我并没有恶意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,只是一不小心把心里想的事情说出口了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是「拿到金奖不也很棒吗」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.44,0:17:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,即便是「无用金奖」也很优秀…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.48,0:17:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,呀 连马尾辫都扎起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.97,0:17:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,第一天就干劲满溢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.09,0:17:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真啰嗦 还有别随便开门进来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.07,0:17:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好好 抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.75,0:17:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,话说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.54,0:17:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,都说了别随便开门进来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你要放弃吹奏乐了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.15,0:17:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？因为你在北宇治啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.87,0:17:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,放弃…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.19,0:18:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,末吉和吉哪个比较好？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是末吉吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.76,0:18:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,从上至下是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.46,0:18:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,大吉 中吉 小吉 吉 半吉 末吉 末小吉这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.16,0:18:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说吉更好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,谢…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我也久违地想求一支签了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.00,0:18:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.56,0:18:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,失礼了 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是运动会上放的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.25,0:18:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好像叫「天堂与地狱」来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,准确地说是「地狱的奥菲欧」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:41.48,Tips,,0,0,0,,{\fs40}注：「地狱的奥菲欧」是雅克·奥芬巴赫所作的轻歌剧，\N1914年初次于日本公演时的日语标题为「天国与地狱」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.67,0:18:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是一首很棒的曲子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那么再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,早餐呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.16,0:20:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.18,0:20:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,吹不出声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那个是从哪里来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.24,0:20:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我买来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,买的？你买了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.28,0:20:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 就只买了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你也太心急了 连乐器都还没决定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,怎样才能吹出声呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,绿是拉低音提琴的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.86,0:20:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,请告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…像这样让嘴唇…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.56,0:21:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样让嘴唇震动哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.37,0:21:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.14,0:21:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,试试看吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.64,0:21:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,然后再对着吹口吹吹看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.37,0:21:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,吹出声了 刚刚吹出声了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.24,0:21:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,出声了 吹出声了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.76,0:21:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是怎么吹的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.13,0:21:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,对了对了 久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.01,0:21:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,一起加入吹奏乐部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.11,0:21:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.55,0:21:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.62,0:21:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.59,0:21:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.41,0:21:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样 我加入了北宇治高中吹奏乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.34,0:22:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 新的乐章开始了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,--------------------------------------------------OP--------------------------------------------------
